title: ASUS ROG DS74 GTX 1060 <30 FPS *Fixed*
body:
Brand new laptop, won't run lol past 30 fps. It isn't my nvidia settings (thats set to 60 htz), and every other game i've tried runs fine. Plz help....{{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}}


Edit: Turns out the "waiting for v-sync" option was on and was causing the whole problem.

replies.body: Yeeeaaaa sometimes that v-sync can become troublesome on some higher end machines. Turning that off was a good first step!
